Hello, Cayman Islands! Hungry? Need essentials? Bento's here for you!

Whether it's food, pharmacy items, pet products, or package deliveries, Bento is your ultimate solution in the Cayman Islands. From satisfying your cravings to delivering everyday essentials, we've got you covered.

WHAT CAN YOU ORDER WITH BENTO?

• Delicious Food: Enjoy a variety of cuisines—Caribbean, Italian, Japanese, Mexican, and more! Craving sushi, pizza, or burgers? Bento delivers it all.
• Pharmacy Essentials: Health and wellness items delivered straight to your door.
• Pet Products: Treat your furry friends with food, toys, and other pet essentials.
• Package Delivery: Send or receive packages conveniently through our reliable delivery service.

WHY BENTO?

• EXPANDED SERVICES: Bento goes beyond food. Whether it's a quick snack or urgent pharmacy items, we're your all-in-one delivery app.
• FIND YOUR FAVORITES FAST: Browse the best restaurants, stores, and services in the Cayman Islands.
• REAL-TIME TRACKING: Track your order from confirmation to delivery in real time.
• SECURE PAYMENTS: Safe and easy payment options you can trust.
• LOCAL FOCUS: Supporting Cayman Islands businesses and creating a stronger, more connected community.

HOW TO USE BENTO?

1. Download the Bento app.
2. Browse restaurants, stores, and services.
3. Select your items and add them to your cart.
4. Choose delivery or pickup.
5. Pay securely and track your order live.

ENJOY A BETTER DELIVERY EXPERIENCE
Bento is designed to make your life easier. With a fresh new app design, it's even simpler to explore options, place orders, and get what you need. From healthy meals to indulgent treats, urgent pharmacy items, or sending packages, Bento does it all.

ABOUT US
Bento is a homegrown technology company connecting the Cayman Islands through seamless delivery services. Starting with food, we've grown to deliver much more—making daily life more convenient while empowering local businesses.

Feeling hungry? Need something delivered? Bento is your go-to app in the Cayman Islands.

Download Bento now and experience effortless delivery.
Visit bento.ky to learn more.

SousChef AI – Your Personal Cooking Assistant

Transform the way you cook with AI-powered recipe discovery and real-time cooking guidance. Snap a photo of any dish to get the recipe,
scan your ingredients for instant meal ideas, or chat with AI to create personalized recipes. Cook with confidence using step-by-step
guidance and live AI assistance.

FEATURES

- Snap a Dish to Get Recipe – See a delicious meal at a restaurant, in a cookbook, or online? Take a photo and instantly get a complete
recipe with ingredients and step-by-step instructions. Our AI identifies the dish and generates professional-quality recipes.
- Snap Ingredients to Get Recipe – Photograph ingredients in your fridge or pantry. AI recognizes everything and suggests multiple
recipes you can make right now. Reduce food waste and never wonder "what can I cook with this?" again.
- Chat to Create Recipes – Describe what you're craving in natural language. "Spicy chicken pasta for 4 people" or "healthy vegetarian
dinner." AI understands your preferences and generates personalized recipes instantly.
- Live AI Cooking Assistant – Get real-time help while you cook. Ask questions about any step, upload photos of your cooking progress for
 instant feedback, and receive guidance tailored to where you are in the recipe.
- Step-by-Step Cooking Mode – Cook with confidence using interactive cooking guidance. Track your progress, check off ingredients, follow
 visual step indicators, and use built-in timers for perfect results every time.
- Adjust Servings Instantly – Scale any recipe from 1 to 12 servings. All ingredient quantities automatically recalculate in real-time.
- Convert Measurements – Toggle between metric and imperial measurements with one tap. All ingredients update instantly across the entire
 app.
- Custom Cookbooks – Organize recipes your way. Create unlimited cookbooks, categorize by cuisine, meal type, or any system that works
for you. Add recipes to multiple collections.
- Visual Cooking Guides – Auto-generated images for complex cooking steps help you visualize techniques and achieve better results.
- Smart Recipe Details – See exactly which ingredients you need for each step (no more scrolling back and forth). Clear time estimates,
skill levels, nutritional information, and emoji icons for visual clarity.

OTHER FEATURES

- Toggle screen lock off while cooking so you can focus in the kitchen.
- Step-specific ingredient lists show what you need right when you need it.
- Temperature guidance with automatic Celsius/Fahrenheit conversion.
- Comprehensive onboarding to personalize recipes based on your dietary preferences, favorite cuisines, and cooking goals.
- Recipe progress tracking across all cooking sessions.
- High-quality generated images for every recipe.
- Optional ingredients clearly marked.
- Interactive tutorials for all features.

HOW DOES IT WORK?

SousChef AI includes both a free version and a subscription version with premium features.

The premium version allows you to:

1. Generate unlimited recipes from dish photos, ingredient scans, and chat.
2. Access unlimited cooking sessions with live AI assistance.
3. Use unlimited photo analysis for cooking feedback.

You can start a 3-day free trial to access these premium features. Unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the free trial,
you will be automatically charged the price indicated on the payment screen for your chosen subscription period. The SousChef AI Premium
subscription renews automatically at the end of each period until you cancel. Canceling your subscription means the automatic renewal
will be disabled. However, you will still have access to all your subscription features for the remaining time of your then-current
period. Note that deleting the app does not cancel your subscriptions.

Yelp has over 135 million reviews of businesses worldwide. Whether you’re looking for a new pizza place to try, a great coffee shop nearby, or need to book a haircut, Yelp is your local guide for finding the perfect place to eat, shop, drink, explore, and relax. The Yelp app is available for iPhone, iPad, and Apple Watch.

Yelp features:

Food Near You - Find Restaurants
• Find the newest and hottest restaurants in your area
• Make reservations, order delivery or pickup—all from your phone
• Filter restaurant search results by price, location, open now, and more

Search for Nearby Businesses, Services, & Professionals
• Discover great local businesses, from hair salons to trusted doctors and movers
• Read millions of reviews by the Yelp community
• Home need repairs? Find the best rated contractors and handymen
• Find great deals offered by local businesses, get quotes instantly, and book appointments

Beauty - Pamper Yourself 
• Find highly-rated salons, spas, massage therapists, and more
• Book appointments through Yelp at the most relaxing staycation destinations

Search Filters 
• Filter your search results by neighborhood, distance, rating, price, and hours of operation
• Look up addresses and phone numbers, call a business, or make reservations directly from the app

Other Features
• Read expert user reviews and browse through beautiful photos of each business
• Write and read reviews, check-in to local businesses, upload photos and add tips for other Yelp users

Find local restaurants, read expert customer reviews, and start searching for businesses near you with Yelp. 

Need Help? Contact Yelp at https://www.yelp-support.com/?l=en_CA
Note: Continued use of GPS running can dramatically decrease battery life.

Find the best slice of pizza using the One Bite app from Barstool Sports. Starting as a video series, Dave “El Presidente” Portnoy has created a cult following of people giving “one bite” pizza reviews by the common man, for the common man. Now you can find all 430+ of Dave’s reviews complete with videos, scores and location. One Bite users can upload their own reviews at any of the 100,000+ restaurants available in the app.

App Features:

Find Pizza
- Find all restaurants (on a map or list) by Score, if reviewed by Dave, delivery support or your bookmarks. 
Get detailed restaurant information like phone number, address, photos, hours and more.

Watch
- See all of Dave's One Bite reviews, tagged to each restaurant. 
- Watch Celebrity and your friends' reviews. 
- Share, like or dislike reviews and follow other reviewers (celebrities and friends alike).

Order
- Order takeout or delivery from the restaurant right from the app. Delivery is supported by Slice, Delivery.com or Yelp!. 

Post a Review
- Upload your own video review giving your One Bite score of any pizza restaurant, rating it from 0 - 10. (Decimal scores supported so there are no amateur reviews)

Profile
- See all of your own reviews including your average rating.

When you want pizza, you really want pizza. Luckily, our app is the quickest and easiest way to order one with a whole host of exclusive features. Want to know more? Course you do…


ORDER PIZZA

Scroll through our easy-order menu and treat yourself to an all-time classic or discover something new! You can even Create Your Own customised creation, give it a name and save it for next time. 


DELIVERY OR TAKEAWAY

Whether you want to collect from your local store or have your pizza delivered to your door, our app’s got you covered. With stores up and down the country, you’re sure to find a Domino’s Pizza near you. 


EXCLUSIVE PIZZA DEALS

If deals are your thing, you’ve come to the right place (almost). Download our app and you’ll find dozens of exclusive pizza deals to suit any budget (and any occasion). You can even add your vouchers to bag discounts on your order!


GROUP ORDERING

If you need to order pizza for the whole fam, you can set up a group order to make ordering for the gang a doddle. Just send them an invite, let them choose what they want and it’ll get added to the order! 


PRE-ORDERING

If you know you want pizza later, but you’re ready to order now…no worries. Get your order in early, let us know when you want it, and we’ll do the rest. Oh, and if you know you want the same as last time, you can just choose it from your order history! 


PAYMENT

Oh, and when it comes to settling up, you can pay pretty much however you like…using card, PayPal or with just a few taps thanks to Apple Pay. Plus, you can keep an eye on your pizza’s progress with our trusty pizza tracker.
 

So, if you haven’t downloaded our app yet, you’re missing out on everything you love about Domino’s and so much more. 

Hit the link to download now and see it with your own eyes!

Order Your Favourite Food with Just 3 Simple Taps!

Serving millions across over 400 cities in 11 Asian markets — Singapore, Hong Kong, Thailand, Malaysia, Pakistan, Taiwan, the Philippines, Bangladesh, Laos, Cambodia, and Myanmar — foodpanda is your go-to for everyday food delivery.

Endless Food and Grocery Delivery Choices at Your Fingertips!

We've got exclusive discounts and promos waiting for all new foodies. With a simple click, your food and groceries are on their way with fast delivery!

Best Food and Grocery Delivery Deals Just for You!

Welcome to My Bar, Unleash Your Inner Bartender with the Ultimate Cocktail Companion!

Your go-to app for discovering and crafting delicious cocktails right at home. Whether you're a cocktail enthusiast eager to explore new recipes or a professional bartender refining your mixology skills, My Bar brings a world of drinks to your fingertips.
Why Choose My Bar?
* Explore Hundreds of Drink Recipes: Dive into a vast collection of cocktail recipes, from timeless classics to innovative new mixes. Whether you're in the mood for a simple highball or an intricate craft concoction, our library has you covered. Search by name or the spirits you love.
* Easy-to-Follow Guides: Our detailed instructions ensure that mixing your favorite drinks is simple and fun, no matter your experience level. Achieve perfect results every time and impress your friends with your bartending skills.
* Filter by Your Ingredients: My Bar’s unique filtering system allows you to input the ingredients you have on hand, offering you a personalized selection of recipes you can make without needing a trip to the store. It's like having a virtual bartender at your disposal.
* Learn and Grow: Elevate your mixology knowledge with My Bar Tutorials.
* Favorite and Track: Save your preferred recipes in a custom list for quick access later. Rate and review your experiments, helping you remember which concoctions you loved most.
* Regular Updates & User-Friendly Design: We continuously enrich My Bar with the latest cocktail trends, seasonal specials, and user-requested features. Coupled with our sleek, intuitive interface, you're set for an unparalleled cocktail crafting experience.

Transform your home into the ultimate cocktail bar with My Bar. Download now and start crafting your next extraordinary drink. Cheers!

We would love to hear your feedback. 

Get in touch if there are any features you would love to add to the app. Drop us an email at - hello@getmybar.co.uk
